svg.text: 我今天 挺 高兴 的。
shows how much the speaker feels a certain
那门课 挺 难 的。
这种音乐 挺 好听 的。
This type of music is quite pleasant.
他 挺 喜欢做运动 的。
(gāoxìng) both mean “happy,” but they are used differently.
(gāoxìng) is used to describe more everyday emotions and cannot be used to
wish someone a happy birthday or a happy holiday.
is often used to describe longer stretches of time (like a happy childhood), as well
as to wish a happy birthday.
